   <name>Adopt A Pet</name>
   <description>Welcome to the Adopt a Pet app. Adoptapet.ie is Ireland's newest and largest pet adoption website. View cats, dogs, horses and more for adoption around Ireland all from the palm of your hand.



Features include:

- Dogs for adoption

- Cats for adoption

- Advice on how to adopt a pet

- Infinite scrolling

- Call rescues directly from within the app

- Email rescues directly from within the app



* Please note this app is new and future versions will include lots more features which we are currently working hard on. 



FEEDBACK:

Your feedback matters to us. Please send any feedback, questions or suggestions to hello@adoptapet.ie</description>
   <author href="http://www.adoptapet.ie" email="damienoneill2001@hotmail.com">AdoptAPet</author>
   
